import { Box, Image, Input, Text, VStack, Button, HStack } from "native-base"
import React from "react"

const Register = () => {
  return (
    <Box flex={1} alignItems="center" justifyContent="center">
      <Image
        style={{ height: 250, width: 250 }}
        mb={10}
        source={require("../../../assets/images/login.png")}
      />
      <Box>
        <Text fontSize="2xl" bold mb={5}>
          Register
        </Text>
        <VStack space={4} mb={10}>
          <Input width={300} placeholder="Email" type="email" />
          <Input width={300} placeholder="Name" type="text" />
          <Input width={300} placeholder="Password" type="password" />
        </VStack>
        <Button width={300} backgroundColor="#FF5555">
          <Text color="white" fontWeight={800}>
            Register
          </Text>
        </Button>
      </Box>
      <HStack space={2} mt={2}>
        <Text>Joined us before?</Text>
        <Text color="#FF5555">Login</Text>
      </HStack>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Register
